des:
Get your very own stoner name from Mr. Tasty Biscuits, the world's oldest stoner. Mr Tasty Biscuits will fire up his Stoner Name Generator and give you and your friends each a memorable stoner name. When you've got a new name, play a quick round of Would Your Rather. 

Mr. Tasty Biscuits is sure to give you some giggles. 

Created by Sparkle Pockets.
